{"tid":1291733,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【會員公告】今日蘋果中午旺角、銅鑼灣、荃灣街站 為你解答疑難！","createTime":"2019-07-07T04:20:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T00:26:27.000Z","uid":78546,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0b09fdcf780f15b0da0b93bf92ef07864191af85","tid":1291733,"uid":78546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T04:20:45.000Z","msg":"近日有部份會員反映在登記成為《蘋果動新聞》升級壹會員的過程中，出現疑難，我們今日（7月7日）中午會在旺角、銅鑼灣及荃灣設置街站，即時解答疑難。如果你有任何疑難或查詢，歡迎到以下地點，我們會有親切的客服大使馬上為你解答！<br />\n<br />\n街站位置：<br />\n1.旺角：旺角豉油街（西洋菜南街交界，荷李活商業中心旁）<br />\n2.銅鑼灣：崇光對出，金百利中心門口<br />\n3.荃灣：荃灣地皇廣場門口（大河道與安榮街交界）<br />\n<br />\n街站開放時間：<br />\n7月7日（星期日）中午12:00-傍晚6:00"},{"pid":"0a20df0bd91518e6ff7d49a902d0d5934c3f342b","tid":1291733,"uid":54181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T04:21:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"54e480f1dd05587c764d4e5e4895fa258419f11d","tid":1291733,"uid":78546,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T04:22:14.000Z","msg":"不如試下直接比3蚊 睇下收唔收<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c1197604e287137c4e6cd3385cb1eea7d178208","tid":1291733,"uid":54181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T04:23:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d2a0fb7cb912789dd0a6b9222998a2d4217b6924","tid":1291733,"uid":78546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T04:34:20.000Z","msg":"我冇野講"},{"pid":"1d633cea000712f9ec6b3f38dd9f0f675ea0165a","tid":1291733,"uid":37596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T04:35:08.000Z","msg":"生果要ON9到幾時<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f21c75b980a7598505a530e1de45b3b5d7a0910c","tid":1291733,"uid":252321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T04:39:08.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 解答之餘，放埋個籌款箱仲撚實際啦"},{"pid":"b7c99003ffb11d2bfdbcff8aae48409f6a341246","tid":1291733,"uid":51720,"lik